By using the experimental values of ?, u, and ?, excess molar volume, , deviations in viscosity, ??, excess free energy of activation for viscous flow, ?G*E, excess molar isentropic compressibility, , deviation of the speeds of sound, uD, from their ideal values uid in an ideal mixtures, apparent molar volume, and apparent molar compressibility,  and  of the components at infinite dilution have been calculated.
